data.description: Welcome to 320 Laurel Ave! This well-maintained home located in the heart of Walterboro has approx. 1400 sq ft. 2 bedrooms, one full and one-half bath. There is Living room,  Separate Dining room, Kitchen comes with stove and refrigerator, large pantry closet and has built- in shelving.  Off of the kitchen is a den and a laundry room with cabinets . Also, there is a room off of the Living room that owners use as an office but could possibly work for a 3rd bedroom. Some recent improvements to the inside are vinyl plank flooring throughout, all new celling fans and lights, painted inside, new dishwasher, Kitchen facet and blown insulation in attic. Moving to the outside there is a large, coved porch off the back of the home for entering family and friends. Also, above ground pool, newprivacy fence around the backyard for privacy, new garage door with remote for the detached garage that has a workshop area, Barn storage building with loft. The HVAC was replaced in 2019 and the roof was just replaced. Call for more information!!
